cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG 

The paper deals with cyber security in the context of fog radio and optical networks (F-RON) in cyber-physical systems (CPS). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning and brain-like knowledge base, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of F-RON also indicates a possible category of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and the application in CPS suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control).
